Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}「真紅」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琅碧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈我們要回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的生氣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點帶著真紅逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類  真紅就拜託你了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個  我不會輕易放過你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我蓋的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的時候  作為暑假作業做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒事  這點小傷根本不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算右手沒了  還有左手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？就算扣子我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經變成了不完美的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了父親大人賜給我的很重要的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經變成廢物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  不要那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經無法當上愛麗絲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有不完美的部分  我也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不會明白的  我已經是個廢物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有資格成為愛麗絲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲是比任何花朵都來得高貴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何寶石都純潔無瑕  一點污垢也沒有的完美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟你們人類不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被要求完美的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會想要一個變成廢物的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  我不認為你是個有缺陷的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算欠缺了什麼  我也會把它補回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我而言  是很重要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了  我會保護你的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純的內心開始產生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛  翠星石  蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下真紅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了櫻田家裡的純的事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學的入學考好像落榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  還被稱為天才  其實根本沒什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不會吧？  真是個討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是記憶之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你痛苦不堪的回憶和過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的能走得過去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你是個更聰明的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  你們通通給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫你的忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單  只要告訴我真紅在哪裡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會告訴你這種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了…我會保護真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不可愛  明明就辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的  你什麼都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你眼裡  我或許看起來像個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不會有任何好處  居然還會這麼拚命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正沒有意義  做了也沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  她們身處這場連有沒有意義都不知道的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍能一直奮戰到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們比我在很久很久以前就深信著  這樣做一定有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼區區的人類能抵擋我的攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是純的夢境哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要純有心的話  他就能戰勝任何敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個僕從終於能派上用場了  純
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…壞掉的東西  居然能修補起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事只有父親大人  或是大師才辦得到才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人類居然辦得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是該分出個勝負的時候了  水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  退到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在  我一定不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到我的後面看著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷裡耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有媒介的你  是不可能贏得了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已經揭曉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦  給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為愛麗絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為愛麗絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  到我的後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了  水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是廢物…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她的身體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個尚未完成的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人在製作她的途中  就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人  為什麼…為什麼要把我做成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明如此深愛著你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要成為…成為愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為父親大人的…完美人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈渴望得到父親大人的愛  所以才想當上愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是靠著這股意志力  沒有媒介也依然在活動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想跟父親大人說  她不需要媒介就能把大家打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己才是最完美的人偶是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許她對父親大人的思念  比誰都更單純吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  卻因此而毀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是純的樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣好小哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用這把剪刀把纏繞在旁邊的雜草剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石再幫他澆水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣放著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這棵樹必須成長茁壯成大樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是旁邊的雜草  當然要靠自己的力量來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己辦得到吧  純
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琅碧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  我們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純與真紅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人應該沒問題的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟有這麼多光芒射進來的說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手指果然附有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  可以讓人覺得很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我當上了愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候  我想請你幫我做一件美麗的長袍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼難做的衣服  我不會做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天你會變成無所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我梳頭髮  然後綁起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要我來？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淑女只讓她心儀的人摸她的頭髮喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該覺得榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  純
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你現在的內心世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片變得非常晴朗的天空也不會一直都晴朗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候會下雨  有時候也會刮起暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色轉變的時候  如果放著不管  說不定就永遠恢復不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候  你就必須持續奮戰不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是活著的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好孩子  純
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走？去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於你的回憶  我會一直存放在心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你也別把我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣質高貴的薔薇少女第五人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  是屬於你的幸福人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！真紅！真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  去叫真紅與小雛  要快點吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了很遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我的份呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那個…那個…你的份？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法  在我回來之前要準備好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…純  你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  歡迎回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼你們會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  怎麼這麼慢才回來  快點去泡茶給我喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你們不是走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人說過那樣的話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠了的說  我要離家出走的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個壞心眼人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  這次是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  電車要開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  外面很冷  把窗戶關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  庫庫偵探要開始演了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才戒指明明不見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們力量使用過度  戒指才會暫時消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  由於你身為人類的能量變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能使戒指重新綻放光輝  讓我回到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  這都多虧了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
